  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open Agent Console from the Service Desk group in the sidebar.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.505,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "One screen, three panes.",
      "startS": 4.071,
      "endS": 5.749,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "The queue on the left,",
      "startS": 6.301,
      "endS": 7.328,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "the live conversation in the middle,",
      "startS": 7.625,
      "endS": 9.206,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "the customer's details on the right.",
      "startS": 9.522,
      "endS": 11.146,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "No tab-hopping while someone waits on you.",
      "startS": 11.66,
      "endS": 13.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Up in the header, your presence.",
      "startS": 14.307,
      "endS": 16.237,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "It reads Offline right now, and it can be Available, Away, Busy, or Offline.",
      "startS": 16.599,
      "endS": 18.571,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "This is how the desk knows whether you're ready for a contact.",
      "startS": 18.834,
      "endS": 20.361,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Leave it where your shift set it; we don't touch it here.",
      "startS": 20.625,
      "endS": 29.12,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Look at the top of the queue.",
      "startS": 29.52,
      "endS": 31.025,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Three numbers give you the load at a glance:",
      "startS": 31.518,
      "endS": 33.748,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "how many are waiting, the average wait, and how many are flagged high priority.",
      "startS": 34.016,
      "endS": 38.318,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "All zero now.",
      "startS": 38.599,
      "endS": 39.539,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "A calm board.",
      "startS": 39.78,
      "endS": 40.719,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "There's a search box over the queue.",
      "startS": 41.205,
      "endS": 42.916,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Type a name, a phone number, a plan, or the reason for the handoff, and the list narrows to it.",
      "startS": 43.402,
      "endS": 48.822,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "On a busy shift, that's how you pull one contact out of a crowd.",
      "startS": 49.719,
      "endS": 53.266,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Three buttons scope the queue.",
      "startS": 53.788,
      "endS": 55.588,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Mine is yours.",
      "startS": 56.043,
      "endS": 57.301,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Unassigned is up for grabs.",
      "startS": 57.675,
      "endS": 59.383,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Team is the whole group's board.",
      "startS": 60.235,
      "endS": 62.104,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Right now it's set to Team, so you're seeing everything, not only your own.",
      "startS": 62.344,
      "endS": 66.397,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Below that, the channels.",
      "startS": 66.889,
      "endS": 68.325,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "All,",
      "startS": 69.109,
      "endS": 69.526,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "then Voice,",
      "startS": 70.014,
      "endS": 70.853,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "S-M-S, and Web.",
      "startS": 71.305,
      "endS": 72.906,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Those last three are the ways a customer reaches you, and All shows them together.",
      "startS": 73.837,
      "endS": 78.278,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Remember the three:",
      "startS": 78.988,
      "endS": 79.841,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "voice, text,",
      "startS": 80.26,
      "endS": 80.784,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "and web chat.",
      "startS": 81.105,
      "endS": 82.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Open the sort control.",
      "startS": 83,
      "endS": 84.24,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "You can work the queue longest wait first, priority first, or most recent first.",
      "startS": 84.737,
      "endS": 89.686,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Longest wait first is the fair choice;",
      "startS": 90.258,
      "endS": 92.504,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "it clears whoever has been holding the longest.",
      "startS": 92.903,
      "endS": 95.154,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Close it without changing anything.",
      "startS": 95.561,
      "endS": 97.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Under the filters, the queue itself.",
      "startS": 97.691,
      "endS": 99.702,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "It says no matching handoffs, because nothing is waiting.",
      "startS": 100.456,
      "endS": 103.707,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "When a contact comes in, its row shows up right here for you to pick up.",
      "startS": 104.346,
      "endS": 108.339,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "The middle is empty too.",
      "startS": 108.8,
      "endS": 110.107,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Select a handoff from the queue, it says, to open its console.",
      "startS": 111.36,
      "endS": 114.978,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "That's the cue.",
      "startS": 115.666,
      "endS": 116.462,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "You click a waiting row, and the conversation loads into this space.",
      "startS": 117.256,
      "endS": 120.96,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "And on the right, the Customer panel.",
      "startS": 121.462,
      "endS": 123.365,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "No conversation selected, for now.",
      "startS": 123.805,
      "endS": 125.692,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Once you open one, this is where the customer's context sits, so you're never guessing who you're helping.",
      "startS": 126.28,
      "endS": 131.715,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "So why is it all empty?",
      "startS": 132.16,
      "endS": 133.574,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "The queue fills when the AI Agent hands a conversation to a person.",
      "startS": 134.433,
      "endS": 138.283,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Those escalations land right here, in the Handoff Queue.",
      "startS": 138.868,
      "endS": 142.268,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "The agent side of that is a later lesson; for now, know this is where a handed-off customer waits for you.",
      "startS": 142.943,
      "endS": 148.878,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "One screen, three panes.",
      "startS": 149.28,
      "endS": 151.081,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "The queue you scope by who owns it and by channel,",
      "startS": 151.444,
      "endS": 154.432,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "the console that opens the conversation,",
      "startS": 154.812,
      "endS": 157.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "and the customer's context beside it.",
      "startS": 157.418,
      "endS": 159.53,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Your presence lives in the header, and you leave it alone unless your shift changes.",
      "startS": 160.194,
      "endS": 164.456,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "That's the Agent Console.",
      "startS": 164.984,
      "endS": 166.696,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}